OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776953470
OL,3,CUndercover sting highlights illegal
OL,4,Ctobacco trade in Grimsby and
OL,5,CCleethorpes
OL,7,FMultiple shops in Grimsby and
OL,8,FCleethorpes have been found to be
OL,9,Fselling illegal tobacco.
OL,11,FTest purchasing of 38 independent
OL,12,Ftobacco retailers was carried out by a
OL,13,Ftrained undercover operative on behalf
OL,14,Fof major tobacco manufacturer JTI UK
OL,15,Fin February.
OL,17,FSome 23 of the shops visited, or 61
OL,18,Fper cent, were found to be selling
OL,19,Fillegal tobacco.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
