PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776953470
OL,3,CUndercover sting highlights illegal
OL,4,Ctobacco trade in Grimsby and
OL,5,CCleethorpes
OL,7,FPolling in January for JTI's 'It Costs
OL,8,FMore Than You Think' campaign against
OL,9,Fthe sale of illegal tobacco found 80
OL,10,Fper cent of residents questioned in
OL,11,Fnorthern Lincolnshire believe there is
OL,12,Fnot enough enforcement.
OL,14,FA freedom of information (FOI) request
OL,15,Fmade by the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,16,FService to the council in November
OL,17,Flast year reveals that between 2021/22
OL,18,Fand 2024/25, illegal and non-compliant
OL,19,Ftobacco products to the value of #1.9m
OL,20,Fwere seized by the council's Trading
OL,21,FStandards team.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
