PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776953470
OL,3,CUndercover sting highlights illegal
OL,4,Ctobacco trade in Grimsby and
OL,5,CCleethorpes
OL,7,FThe council carried out 172 visits of
OL,8,Fretailers between 2021 and November
OL,9,F2025 on suspicion of involvement in
OL,10,Fthe sale of illegal or non-compliant
OL,11,Ftobacco products.
OL,13,FAmong products bought during the
OL,14,Fundercover operation were counterfeit
OL,15,FAmber Leaf 50g for #5 and contraband
OL,16,FEsse cigarettes for #4. In January,
OL,17,Fthe recommended retail price for a
OL,18,Flegal 30g pouch of Amber Leaf was
OL,19,F#27.95.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
